# Room 31 JavaScript Essentials 

## Task 1 Introduction

Objective: Set up the lab environment and understand the basics of JavaScript.
Start the Target Machine in the VM to run exercises.
JavaScript (JS) adds interactivity to HTML/CSS websites (validation, onClick actions, animations).
This room introduces JS fundamentals from a cybersecurity perspective, showing how attackers can abuse legitimate features.
Prerequisites: Linux Fundamentals, Web Application Basics, How Websites Work.
Learning Goals:
- Basics of JS.
- Integrating JS into HTML.
- Abusing dialogue functions.
- Bypassing control flow.
