## Task 2 Essential Concepts

- Objective: Learn core building blocks of JavaScript.
- Variables: Declared with var, let, const.
- Data Types: string, number, boolean, null, undefined, object.
- Functions: Group reusable code. Example: PrintResult(rollNum).
- Loops: Repeat tasks (for, while, do...while). Example: iterate through roll numbers to print results.

